Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Narrator,Radio,0,0,0,,A
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.82,0:00:10.49,Narrator,Radio,0,0,0,,{\an8}It's Morioh Radio!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.90,0:00:14.95,Narrator,Radio,0,0,0,,{\an8}Coming at you once again is yours truly, Kai Harada.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.95,0:00:17.03,Narrator,Radio,0,0,0,,{\an8}To get you up to speed, last week's topic was...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.03,0:00:23.46,Narrator,Radio,0,0,0,,{\an8}"The King of Terror is supposed to come from the sky this July. \NWhat are the citizens of Morioh to do?"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.46,0:00:24.96,Narrator,Radio,0,0,0,,{\an8}All right, let's get to the replies.
Comment: 0,0:00:25.33,0:00:27.29,Narrator,Radio,0,0,0,,{\an8}This one's from "RIP Bro." {Okuyasu, lol}
Comment: 0,0:00:27.29,0:00:28.67,Narrator,Radio,0,0,0,,{\an8}What could have happened to his bro?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.78,0:00:19.20,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Check out how my spokes shine while they spin!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.20,0:00:22.46,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,I got this mountain bike as a gift for getting into high school!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.46,0:00:24.96,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Getting new stuff is always so exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.96,0:00:28.67,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Guess this means I won't be taking the bus for a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.48,0:00:44.94,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,O-Oww...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.94,0:00:46.48,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Wh-What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.06,0:00:49.19,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Someone left a bag in the middle of the road...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.95,0:00:56.91,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,N-No way! The thing inside that bag was a...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.12,0:01:04.41,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Wh-What am I gonna do?! I ran it over!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.41,0:01:06.25,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,I-It was just an accident!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.25,0:01:07.88,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,It was right in the middle of the road!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.88,0:01:09.63,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,I couldn't help it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.63,0:01:11.67,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.67,0:01:14.05,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,That wasn't your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.05,0:01:16.26,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,It was just an unfortunate accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.47,0:01:23.73,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,Whoever left that kitten inside a bag\N in the middle of the road is to blame.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.73,0:01:26.31,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,It's pretty horrific, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.85,0:01:28.98,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,W-We have to help it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.98,0:01:30.32,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,Too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.32,0:01:33.19,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,You don't hear any crying, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.19,0:01:34.57,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,It died.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.70,0:01:37.32,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.32,0:01:43.29,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,My name's Kobayashi Tamami, and I just so happened to \Ngraduate from the same school as you two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.79,0:01:45.87,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,Nice bike you got there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.16,0:01:47.37,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,You a first-year?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.62,0:01:51.46,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah... My name is Hirose Koichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.46,0:01:55.09,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,Man, that takes me back. High school was the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.09,0:01:57.01,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,Things were great back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.01,0:02:00.60,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,Anyway, have a seat, Hirose, my pal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.60,0:02:02.85,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Huh? B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.77,0:02:07.60,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,C'mon, be quiet and have a seat!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.64,0:02:12.36,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,So, I got a proposition for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.77,0:02:18.53,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,I can bury that kitten for you,\N but you'll have to give me a bit of cash in exchange. Sound good?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.36,0:02:21.66,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,Hey! You listening to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.66,0:02:23.37,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Wh-What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.37,0:02:25.95,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,C'mon kid, quit yanking my chain.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.95,0:02:27.50,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,I know this wasn't your fault...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.50,0:02:31.63,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,...but are you really gonna do nothing about killing my cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.13,0:02:33.96,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Are you telling me that was {\i1}your{\i0} cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.96,0:02:35.84,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,Sure was!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.84,0:02:39.63,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Y-You put your kitten in a place like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.63,0:02:42.26,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,We're way past that, my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.26,0:02:45.64,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,I just wanna know if you really plan to do nothing about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.93,0:02:50.48,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,After all, you're the one who killed it, kid!
Comment: 0,0:02:52.02,0:02:52.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Opening
Comment: 0,0:04:07.47,0:04:07.51,Main,,0,0,0,,B
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.51,0:04:12.27,Title Part 4 Episode 2,sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(654,476)\pos(130,880)\fs60}Episode 6: {\fs80} Hirose Koichi (Echoes)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.26,0:04:11.02,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,{\an8}So, you're probably feeling pretty guilty about this, am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.02,0:04:16.86,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,{\an8}If spending a little cash would\N free your heart from the shackles of guilt...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.11,0:04:20.61,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,...you'd be stupid not to do it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.61,0:04:21.69,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.53,0:04:32.54,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Wh-What's this lock-thing in my chest?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.41,0:04:34.29,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,It's so heavy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.29,0:04:37.17,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,Huh? You can see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.63,0:04:42.47,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,Heh, then this should be quick, Hirose, my pal!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.47,0:04:44.80,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Th-This is a Stand!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.80,0:04:48.97,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,There's a Stand lodged inside my chest!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.52,0:04:52.31,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Hey, Josuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.31,0:04:55.90,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Ain't that Koichi over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.90,0:04:59.19,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's definitely him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.19,0:05:03.15,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,He's always hanging around real shady-looking types.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.15,0:05:05.78,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Looks like he's havin' fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.78,0:05:13.04,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,I'll have you know, I got my ability from a guy\N named Nijimura Keicho just four months ago. {obtained was too formal for this sleezebag}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.04,0:05:16.58,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,I couldn't tell you why it happened, but I've been happy ever since!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.58,0:05:22.00,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,If I take advantage of my ability while I'm young, \NI'll be set for the rest of my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.00,0:05:22.84,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,Anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.84,0:05:24.67,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,Hurry and cough it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.67,0:05:28.59,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,This lock isn't going anywhere until you pay up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.59,0:05:30.47,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,I-I'm all out...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.43,0:05:32.85,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,...of money...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.22,0:05:36.39,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,Huh? Did you really just look away from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.39,0:05:38.31,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.52,0:05:42.32,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,I-It became heavier!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.32,0:05:44.69,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,I'm gonna fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.19,0:05:46.82,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,Tsk, tsk, tsk!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.20,0:05:49.57,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,Lying like that isn't very nice of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.57,0:05:53.24,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,You felt pretty guilty doing that, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.24,0:05:57.42,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,The guiltier you feel, the bigger my lock becomes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.42,0:06:00.42,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,It represents the weight of your sins.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.42,0:06:02.30,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,It's automatic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.30,0:06:07.34,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,Even if I'm asleep, or really far away, it won't ever come off!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.63,0:06:10.55,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,Get it? Now you'd best be coughing up your wallet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.55,0:06:11.35,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.14,0:06:15.31,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,Are you for real? \NYou should have just given it to me in the first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.31,0:06:17.77,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,You've even got seven thousand yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.77,0:06:22.48,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,I-I need it to buy new sneakers for gym class today...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.48,0:06:24.40,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,Sneakers?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.57,0:06:26.90,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,Go barefoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.70,0:06:30.36,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,What's going on over here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.45,0:06:35.49,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,J-Josuke and Okuyasu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.49,0:06:39.25,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,A grown man trying to threaten a high school kid for money?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.25,0:06:41.67,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,How about you find a job and make your own money?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.67,0:06:45.09,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,Hold it! Mind your own business, kiddos!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.09,0:06:47.38,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,That ain't happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.38,0:06:51.09,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,If there's trashy Stand users around, \Nabusing the power of their Stands...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.09,0:06:54.14,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,...they need to be taken out with the rest of the garbage.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.14,0:06:54.81,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.81,0:06:58.35,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,This thing's really wedged in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.14,0:07:01.81,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,Whoa, hold on... You guys can see it, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.81,0:07:03.77,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,Just how many people around here can?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.77,0:07:06.28,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,That's what I'd like to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.28,0:07:08.53,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,But right now, it doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.53,0:07:11.45,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Will you please remove the lock from his chest?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.57,0:07:15.99,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,Hey, you goddamn brats! Don't underestimate me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.24,0:07:18.95,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,I'm not messing around here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.95,0:07:25.50,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,Sinners have to pay for their sins! It's a rule of society!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.50,0:07:29.63,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,How about this? \NWhy don't you two pay me in Koichi's stead?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.63,0:07:31.63,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,I'll let him off the hook if you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.76,0:07:34.55,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,Money is money, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.55,0:07:38.31,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Oh? Tryin' t'pull a fast one?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.31,0:07:39.56,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Fuckin' try me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.56,0:07:43.23,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Hold on a second! You already took seven thousand yen from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.23,0:07:45.98,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,Consider it a fee for lying to my face, idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.61,0:07:51.70,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,You think seven thousand yen is enough \Nto make up for taking the life of my poor kitten?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.70,0:07:53.28,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,That just won't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.28,0:07:55.49,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,Five hundred thousand should be enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.49,0:07:57.41,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Five hundred thousand?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.87,0:08:00.37,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,Of course, five hun{\fscx300}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.79,0:08:02.37,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Shut the fuck up, stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.04,0:08:04.25,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,O-Okuyasu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.25,0:08:05.84,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Hey, don't push it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.84,0:08:08.55,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,An' keep your fuckin' mouth shut, dumbass!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.55,0:08:12.43,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,We toldja t'give his money back, so cough it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.60,0:08:28.69,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,O-Oww! My front tooth!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.44,0:08:34.28,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,H-Hey, whydja stumble around an' fall on purpose like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.28,0:08:37.41,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,"On purpose"? You're awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.41,0:08:40.54,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,How could you say something like that after hitting me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.29,0:08:46.38,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,You knocked out my front tooth! You're the worst!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.38,0:08:50.25,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,H-Hey, hold up, buddy... You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.25,0:08:50.25,Secondary,Koichi,0,0,0,,W-Wait, Okuyasu...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.25,0:08:53.76,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Don't let him make you feel guilty for what you did!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.64,0:08:59.31,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,H-He did it on purpose!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.14,0:09:03.64,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,Repairing a front tooth is pretty expensive, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.64,0:09:06.06,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,Doesn't help that my insurance won't cover it! {Xemnas: The main reason Japs don't fix their teeth is because most insurance plans that aren't ridiculously expensive don't cover dental, so it's just too expensive.}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.52,0:09:09.02,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Y-Ya no good...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.02,0:09:12.03,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,Take it easy! Don't try anything funny with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.03,0:09:19.20,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,If anyone with one of my locks attached to them tries to hurt me, \Nthe damage gets sent right back!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.78,0:09:21.62,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,D-Dickhead...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.37,0:09:28.54,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Hey. Is this supposed to be the cat Koichi ran over?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.71,0:09:33.63,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,A-A stuffed animal?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.34,0:09:38.84,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Here, let me have a look.\N I picked up your front tooth for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.05,0:09:41.51,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,All better, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.06,0:09:47.98,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,It's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.98,0:09:51.07,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,He did it! My chest feels so much lighter!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.07,0:09:53.69,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,Wh-Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.69,0:09:55.99,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Hey, what about that seven thousand yen?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.99,0:09:59.41,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,D-Don't worry about it! I'll give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.74,0:10:03.20,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,We got the money, so fuck off, stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.41,0:10:09.63,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Y-You saved me... Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.13,0:10:12.92,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Th-The bills... H-He took them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.92,0:10:15.97,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,He took the bigger parts so the bank would exchange them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.97,0:10:18.18,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Th-That asshole!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.18,0:10:21.05,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Fuckin' scumbag! An' it ain't even my money...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.27,0:10:26.93,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,Crap! Only got away with seven thousand yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.94,0:10:30.90,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,Don't think you've seen the last of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.90,0:10:32.40,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,Just you wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.70,0:10:49.12,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Having such a rough start this morning really ruined my day...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.12,0:10:50.92,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,I'm back, Police.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.71,0:10:54.09,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Hey, you alive? Woof, woof!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.75,0:10:55.96,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.96,0:10:59.76,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,Oh, you wouldn't believe the wonderful things I've heard about you around town, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.76,0:11:03.51,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,They say you're the epitome of beauty, compassion, and elegance!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.72,0:11:05.93,Main,Mom,0,0,0,,You must be joking!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.93,0:11:07.85,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,I'm most certainly not!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.85,0:11:09.02,Main,Mom,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.02,0:11:10.73,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,Absolutely!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.81,0:11:18.78,Thoughts,Koichi,0,0,0,,Wh-What is he doing inside my house \Nrubbing my mom's shoulders?!
Comment: 0,0:11:20.99,0:11:21.03,Main,,0,0,0,,C
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.78,0:11:27.24,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Y-You!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.24,0:11:28.95,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.95,0:11:32.79,Main,Mom,0,0,0,,Oh, Munchkin, you're home! Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.79,0:11:36.46,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,D-Don't make me ask again! Wh-Why are you here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.46,0:11:41.09,Main,Mom,0,0,0,,This kind man came here to return the money you dropped earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.09,0:11:41.76,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.01,0:11:44.09,Main,Mom,0,0,0,,You rushed home and lost seven thousand yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.09,0:11:48.10,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Th-This money... You told my mom you found it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.10,0:11:53.65,Main,Mom,0,0,0,,That's right. \NYou ran into Mr. Kobayashi on your bike today, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.65,0:11:54.69,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Wha{\fscx300}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.69,0:11:57.40,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,You should thank me for returning your money, Koichi, my pal. {BDs: This is a bit long for 2.71s. Shorten if possible?}{Did my best, past Fadeout :D}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.40,0:11:59.23,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Th-That's just common decency!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.23,0:12:01.99,Main,Mom,0,0,0,,Munchkin, why are you acting so abrasive?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.53,0:12:06.99,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,Ma'am, it's difficult for me to say this, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.49,0:12:12.87,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,...when I ran into your son, \NI seem to have dropped my own wallet in the process.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.17,0:12:15.92,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,It looks exactly like this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.92,0:12:20.42,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,To put it mildly, somehow we swapped wallets.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.42,0:12:23.55,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,Do you get what I'm saying, ma'am?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.55,0:12:27.05,Main,Mom,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, though that seems so unlike him...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.05,0:12:28.56,Main,Mom,0,0,0,,But I suppose it's possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.56,0:12:34.14,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,In that case, would you please ask your son\N to return my wallet to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.19,0:12:38.19,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,I had about five hundred thousand yen in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.19,0:12:40.57,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,Please have him return it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.57,0:12:42.11,Main,Mom,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.11,0:12:44.45,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,F-Five hundred thousand?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.45,0:12:46.12,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,So that's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.12,0:12:47.20,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,I know what you're up to!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.20,0:12:48.95,Main,Mom,0,0,0,,M-Munchkin...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.95,0:12:51.95,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Don't panic! He's a con artist!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.95,0:12:53.91,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.95,0:12:53.91,Secondary,Koichi,0,0,0,,It's all lies!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.91,0:12:58.75,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,I can prove that our wallets were switched around.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.75,0:13:03.63,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,Last night, I got a hamburger combo at Jonny's... and...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.63,0:13:08.05,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,Right! I also had an order of onion gratin soup.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.05,0:13:12.10,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,So I believe the total on the receipt should be 1,833 yen...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.10,0:13:15.89,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,It should be tucked away in the wallet with Koichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.57,0:13:28.91,Main,Mom,0,0,0,,M-Munchkin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.91,0:13:31.33,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,N-No! Mom, you have to believe me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.33,0:13:32.87,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,He's trying to trick you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.87,0:13:34.20,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,You hid it there earlier, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.20,0:13:37.62,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Then you went out and bought a similar looking wallet!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.17,0:13:44.42,Main,Tama,0,0,0,,I hate to break it to you, but your son seems to be going through a pretty despicable phase of his life!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.42,0:13:50.76,Main,Tama,0,0,0,,Don't you feel guilty as his mother for raising a son like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.76,0:13:52.01,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.35,0:13:58.85,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,M-Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.81,0:14:01.48,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,I finally did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.48,0:14:06.15,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,Now the weight of her guilt will keep her heart locked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.15,0:14:08.36,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,I'm gonna take you for everything you've got!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.11,0:14:14.20,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,I'll start by taking your house's land, title, and seal!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.20,0:14:17.71,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,It's such a nice house, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.96,0:14:22.54,Main,Sister,0,0,0,,Koichi, is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.25,0:14:24.80,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.80,0:14:27.26,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.97,0:14:33.64,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,When she brought me my tea earlier,\N I made her spill some of it on my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.26,0:14:38.60,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,Then I pretended like it really burned, \Nand she was all like "I'm sorry! I'm so sorry!"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.48,0:14:41.90,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,It was pretty cute and sexy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.90,0:14:44.44,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,She's a third-year at an all-girls school, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.11,0:14:47.65,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,R-Ripe for the picking!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.74,0:14:50.66,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,F-F-Fantastic!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.04,0:14:59.21,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.54,0:15:03.34,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,You won't get away with this! I won't let you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.63,0:15:05.09,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.09,0:15:08.34,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,What's up with that puny egg-thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.10,0:15:20.73,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,What the hell is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.23,0:15:23.81,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Mom, Sis, I need you to leave the room for a bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.81,0:15:25.27,Main,Mom,0,0,0,,Munchkin, what's happening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.27,0:15:27.44,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,This isn't the time for questions!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.44,0:15:31.45,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,Hey! K-Keep that thing away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.45,0:15:38.50,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,Your mom and sister leaving the room \Ndoesn't change the fact that th-they're my hostages!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.71,0:15:47.42,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,I won't let you harm my mom {\i1}or{\i0} my sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.42,0:15:50.47,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,J-Just try it, Koichi! Just try!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.47,0:15:52.47,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Remove their locks, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.47,0:15:59.98,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,If your mom sees you beat the crap out of me, \Nit will only make her feel even guiltier!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.98,0:16:02.23,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,I told you to remove them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.23,0:16:06.90,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,Don't underestimate Kobayashi Tamami, you annoying little shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.90,0:16:09.48,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,L-Like hell I'll take them off!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.57,0:16:16.83,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.83,0:16:18.24,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,That didn't hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.24,0:16:18.99,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.62,0:16:23.00,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,Whoa! What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.00,0:16:25.63,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,That's an impressive sound, but it's so weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.29,0:16:28.42,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,What the hell is with your Stand?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.84,0:16:33.80,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,This thing isn't really fast {\i1}or{\i0} strong, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.80,0:16:37.43,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,How dare you scare me like that, dumbass!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.93,0:16:44.77,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,I'll show you! \NYour Stand's strength is directly related to your mental strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.77,0:16:47.81,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,Which means your mental strength is nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.81,0:16:52.07,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,I'm gonna make sure you pay dearly for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.73,0:16:52.07,Secondary,Koichi,0,0,0,,Something weird is going on with his cheek...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.49,0:16:53.90,Thoughts,Koichi,0,0,0,,"Ka-crack"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.24,0:16:56.99,Thoughts,Koichi,0,0,0,,It looks like some kind of comic book sound effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.87,0:17:06.63,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,Wh-What the hell? There's some weird ringing in my ear!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.63,0:17:09.09,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,It's the same sound from when he hit me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.75,0:17:12.80,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,What the hell is this writing on my arm?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.34,0:17:15.26,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,I-It won't come off!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.64,0:17:26.52,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,W-Wait... Th-These sounds that I hear coming from inside me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.52,0:17:29.44,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,Your Stand did this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.69,0:17:34.32,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,Goddammit! Get rid of these sounds!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.04,0:17:44.08,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,It's sound!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.08,0:17:48.08,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,My Stand is making sounds reverberate inside his body!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.08,0:17:53.67,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,C-Come to think of it, it reminds me of that famous Matsuo Basho poem I learned at school...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.67,0:17:54.88,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,"So quiet and still...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.88,0:17:55.92,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,...the shrill of the cicadas...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.92,0:17:57.38,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,...seeps into the rocks."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.05,0:18:02.39,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,Dammit! I totally fell for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.39,0:18:05.89,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,I'll only stop the sounds if you remove the locks from my mom and sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.89,0:18:11.32,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,If you keep resisting, \Neven I don't know what will happen to your body!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.40,0:18:13.82,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,Stop the sounds!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.36,0:18:20.16,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Quit being stubborn and remove the locks!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.16,0:18:25.16,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,Dammit! How could you do something so horrible to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.20,0:18:31.00,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,I wouldn't threaten and con people\N if I was afraid of little shitheads like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.00,0:18:36.30,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,The "Tama" in my name means "ballsy"! \NLet me show you how I live up to that name! {Add translation note here: "Tama" means "ball" and is slang for the testicles.} {I don't think it's necessary since he's literally telling you what the "Tama" in his name means. In fact, it might even be extra confusing if a TL note says it means something OTHER than what the character is saying. -Fadeout4}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.18,0:18:41.85,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,I'm not scared of some knife!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.85,0:18:43.72,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,Don't take me lightly!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.72,0:18:46.31,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,Prepare to see just how terrifying I can really be!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.31,0:18:48.77,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,The true power of the locks!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.60,0:18:53.61,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Oww!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.94,0:18:52.11,Secondary,Koichi,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.61,0:18:55.98,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,Oww, oww, oww, oww!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.90,0:19:00.45,Thoughts,Tamami,0,0,0,,Make the cut shallow, and scream like hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.45,0:19:01.11,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,Catch!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.11,0:19:02.07,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,"Catch"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.32,0:19:03.45,Main,Mom,0,0,0,,Who was just screaming?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.45,0:19:04.33,Main,Sister,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.83,0:19:06.83,Main,Sister,0,0,0,,Munchkin?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.83,0:19:08.46,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,I-It's not what it looks like!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.71,0:19:12.29,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,O-Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.29,0:19:14.13,Thoughts,Tamami,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.00,0:19:19.26,Main,Mom,0,0,0,,M-Munchkin! How could you do something so horrific?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.26,0:19:23.43,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,No, Mom! It's not what it looks like!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.14,0:19:23.43,Secondary,Sis,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.43,0:19:25.14,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.14,0:19:29.18,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,I win! You lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.18,0:19:31.85,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,Now hurry and get rid of these sounds, Koichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.85,0:19:37.78,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,If you don't stop them now, \Nyour mother won't be able to bear the weight of her guilt!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.36,0:19:44.53,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,When people have more guilt than they can bear, \Nthey start to think they'd be better off dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.62,0:19:49.04,Main,Mom,0,0,0,,I-I can't take it... anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.04,0:19:49.91,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.91,0:19:52.08,Main,Mom,0,0,0,,I've had enough of this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.08,0:19:54.04,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,Enough of the tough guy act!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.04,0:19:57.09,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,Hurry and stop the sounds before your mom kills herself!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.09,0:19:59.17,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,No, I won't stop them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.17,0:20:01.88,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,I'll do the exact opposite and make more!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.93,0:20:04.14,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Believe me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.56,0:20:11.73,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.27,0:20:15.61,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,I need you to believe me, Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.61,0:20:18.11,Note,Sfx,0,0,0,,Text: Believe me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.06,0:20:18.11,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Believe me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.11,0:20:19.48,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.82,0:20:20.99,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Believe me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.48,0:20:26.87,Note,Sfx,0,0,0,,Text: Believe me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.78,0:20:26.12,Thoughts,Tamami,0,0,0,,My ability affects a person's very spirit! \NLike hell she'll believe you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.12,0:20:29.08,Main,Koi,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.62,0:20:33.54,Main,Mom,0,0,0,,He's right... If I, his own mother, won't believe in him...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.54,0:20:36.13,Main,Mom,0,0,0,,...then who will?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.13,0:20:39.17,Main,Mom,0,0,0,,Koichi has always been a good boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.17,0:20:43.05,Main,Mom,0,0,0,,He would never hurt someone or try to take their money!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.05,0:20:44.43,Thoughts,Koichi,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.43,0:20:46.72,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,Th-This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.85,0:20:51.85,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.85,0:20:53.44,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,G-Goddammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.44,0:20:55.19,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,They never would have believed me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.19,0:20:58.06,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,My parents {\i1}never{\i0} would have believed me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.65,0:20:59.57,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,Gulp...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.57,0:21:07.57,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,I was just joking around!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.33,0:21:12.95,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,Munchkin, you gotta believe me \Nwhen I say this was all just a joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.46,0:21:15.46,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Remove my sister's lock, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.46,0:21:17.63,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,It's already off!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.63,0:21:20.96,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,Wouldn't want to do anything to ruin \Nher picturesque beauty, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.96,0:21:24.34,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,I was only joking about taking your house!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.34,0:21:28.22,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,I even gave back your seven thousand yen, didn't I?\N Right? Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.22,0:21:32.60,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,Please forgive me! I'll do anything for you, Master Koichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.60,0:21:34.60,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Huh? You'll do anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.60,0:21:38.44,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,Yes, Master Koichi! Anything! I'll be your underling!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.69,0:21:40.86,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Good. In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.69,0:21:45.07,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Bring me five hundred thousand yen by tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.32,0:21:51.20,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,I'm joking! It was just a joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.45,0:21:58.63,Thoughts,Tamami,0,0,0,,Th-That didn't sound like a joke at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.84,0:22:07.18,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,H-Hey, Okuyasu! What the hell is going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.43,0:22:09.93,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,Allow me to carry your bag to school!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.93,0:22:12.26,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,You're seriously going to carry it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.26,0:22:14.18,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,Why, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.18,0:22:16.94,Main,Tamami,0,0,0,,Master Koichi! You're a true man among men!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.94,0:22:19.15,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,C'mon, cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.69,0:22:20.77,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Hey, Okuyasu!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.77,0:22:24.86,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Fuck if I know! I ain't so smart, remember?
